parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: And we said we would think about it,

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: and the nurses kept looking for us,

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: wherever we were, as if we were delinquents.

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: They even said to do it without telling your husband.

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: ‘Your husband probably wants you to be filled with children”...

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: And that’s how they forced us.

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: They forced us because we were weak

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: they forced us to get that ligation.

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: As we speak in our land,

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: They sent us home without treatment for nothing,

parameter.name: Text
parameter.value: Now they have left us incapacitated,
